700601f-a.title: Bronx: Bronx Boulevard - Duncomb Street
700601f-a.text:
Bronx Boulevard (vantage point), east side, north of Duncomb Street. The view is southeastward across part of the Bronx River
Parkway park area.
June 16, 1938.
P. L. Sperr.
